## Scaling Summary

| Property | Before Scaling | After Scaling |
|----------|---------------|---------------|
| Resolution | 1280 × 720 | 384 × 216 |
| Aspect Ratio | 16:9 | 16:9 (preserved) |
| File size | ~1.2 MB/frame | ~85 KB/frame |
| Labels valid? | Yes | Yes (no change needed) |
| Total disk (train) | ~120 MB | ~8.5 MB |

